- 1.4.0 | Mar 31 2026:

-- New Features --
[New] Reusable CI workflow: file-groups input for multi-container test splitting
      (default 1 = all files in one job, backward compatible — consumers opt in
      with file-groups: N to distribute .bats files round-robin across N matrix jobs)
[New] Setup job: generates matrix JSON — passthrough os-only matrix for file-groups=1,
      round-robin distribution via file-groups.sh for file-groups>1

-- Changes --
[Change] Test job: matrix sourced from setup output, TEST_TARGET falls back to
      test-path when files not specified, artifact naming adds -g{N} suffix for
      grouped runs, concurrency group includes group number
